WEBVTT

00:01.535 --> 00:07.206
♪ ♪

00:10.845 --> 00:13.645
Morgan Freeman: This is
where it all began for me.

00:13.681 --> 00:15.848
My acting career.

00:15.883 --> 00:17.416
When I was in the third grade,

00:17.451 --> 00:20.819
my mother agreed to let
me be in the school play.

00:20.855 --> 00:25.024
I was to play the title
role; "Little boy blue."

00:25.326 --> 00:29.328
It would be my
first time on stage.

00:30.398 --> 00:35.701
The moment came, I
stepped up onto the stage,

00:35.736 --> 00:38.003
into the light.

00:38.039 --> 00:43.976
And the words and the
action flowed effortlessly.

00:44.712 --> 00:46.812
I was only eight years old,

00:46.847 --> 00:49.448
but I knew this was my calling,

00:49.483 --> 00:52.751
this was my destiny.

00:52.787 --> 00:57.956
People say the same thing
about politicians, athletes.

01:00.694 --> 01:03.195
It happens in religion too.

01:03.230 --> 01:07.466
Almost ever faith has a
figure that they think was

01:07.501 --> 01:10.702
chosen by god.

01:10.871 --> 01:13.806
Muslims have Muhammad.

01:13.841 --> 01:16.075
Christians have Jesus.

01:16.110 --> 01:20.679
Jews have Moses and Abraham.

01:20.714 --> 01:25.017
Why do we rally around
these chosen ones?

01:25.052 --> 01:28.954
And how do they guide our faith?

01:31.892 --> 01:33.959
I'm setting out to
meet chosen people who

01:33.994 --> 01:37.463
walk the earth today.

01:37.598 --> 01:40.065
An American boy who's
the reincarnation of

01:40.101 --> 01:42.201
a Buddhist lama.

01:42.236 --> 01:45.270
Jalue: When I grow up I can
teach a lot of people peace.

01:45.306 --> 01:47.206
Morgan Freeman: A
man who heard god Cal him

01:47.241 --> 01:50.909
in his darkest hour.

01:51.679 --> 01:56.849
Kenneth bae: This is when
I felt that god spoke to me.

01:56.984 --> 02:00.686
Morgan Freeman: And a
guru who is no longer human.

02:00.721 --> 02:04.256
Mandeep kaur samra:
It cannot be corrupted.

02:05.826 --> 02:07.526
Morgan Freeman:
I'll try to understand how

02:07.561 --> 02:09.461
chosen ones change us.

02:09.497 --> 02:12.164
Nadim nassar: The memory
of imam hussain it is a

02:12.199 --> 02:16.935
responsibility for
the whole of humanity.

02:17.171 --> 02:19.171
Morgan Freeman: How
they give us strength.

02:19.206 --> 02:22.007
Karudee chotithamaporn: The
deity possess the medium.

02:22.042 --> 02:23.142
They are not themselves.

02:23.177 --> 02:25.310
Dr. Andreas Schneider: The
medium becomes godlike.

02:25.346 --> 02:28.413
Morgan Freeman: To achieve
what seems impossible.

02:28.616 --> 02:29.860
Chief arvol: They're not
going to back down and

02:29.884 --> 02:32.618
we're not
gonna back down either.

02:32.653 --> 02:34.753
Morgan Freeman: And
perhaps even change the

02:34.788 --> 02:37.689
course of history.

02:41.539 --> 02:44.539
