03:04.084 --> 03:08.086
where do you find a chosen one?

03:08.122 --> 03:11.423
In the deserts of Arabia?

03:11.659 --> 03:14.426
In the holy land?

03:15.062 --> 03:18.397
Amid the temples of India?

03:18.832 --> 03:22.367
I found one in the
suburbs of Minnesota.

03:30.110 --> 03:33.011
I've come to the home
of a Tibetan couple who moved

03:33.047 --> 03:35.981
to America in 1999.

03:36.016 --> 03:37.093
Dorje tsegyal: How are you?

03:37.117 --> 03:38.395
Morgan Freeman:
I am very well indeed.

03:38.419 --> 03:39.451
Thank you so much.

03:39.486 --> 03:40.919
Dorje tsegyal: Very good.

03:40.955 --> 03:43.822
Morgan Freeman: Dorje tsegyal
and his wife dechen wangmo.

03:43.857 --> 03:45.390
Dechen wangmo:
Hi, how are you?

03:45.426 --> 03:48.694
Morgan Freeman: Very well.

